title: OnePlus Ace 6T debuts with Snapdragon 8 Gen 5 SoC and 8,300mAh battery
description: After weeks of teasers, OnePlus has officially launched the Ace 6T in China. It happens to be the first phone to be powered by the recently announced Snapdragon 8 Gen 5 chipset. It is currently available for order in China and is expected to debut globally as…
